CASE
  WHEN LOWER(TRIM(PRRCDJ)) = 'null'
  OR TRIM(PRRCDJ) = ''
  OR TRIM(PRRCDJ) = '0' THEN NULL
  ELSE to_timestamp (
     substring(
      CAST(
        date_add(
          concat(
            substring(
              CAST(CAST(TRIM(PRRCDJ) AS INT) + 1900000 AS STRING),
              1,
              4
            ),
            '-01-01'
          ),
          CAST(
            substring(
              CAST(CAST(TRIM(PRRCDJ) AS INT) + 1900000 AS string),
              5,
              8
            ) AS INT
          ) -1
        ) AS STRING
      ),
      1,
      10
    ),
    'yyyy-MM-dd'
  )
END
